### Get all invoices
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/financeservice/Invoices
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new invoice
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/financeservice/Invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "InvoiceNumber": "INV-1001",
  "CustomerName": "ABC Corp",
  "Country": "Germany",
  "Amount": 1200.50,
  "Currency": "EUR",
  "Status_Status": "Pending",
  "IssueDate": "2025-08-01",
  "DueDate": "2025-09-01",
  "RelatedSegment_SegmentName": "Consumer"
}

### Update invoice status
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/financeservice/Invoices/changeStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "InvoiceID": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "Status": "Approved"
}

### Delete invoice
DELETE http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/financeservice/Invoices(11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)
Content-Type: application/json
